 40→          }
 41→          p {
 42→            +"""
 43→                   The problem is: what happens when the underlying content changes?
 44→                   All relevant URLs referencing specific lines will need to be checked, and sometimes
 45→                   adjusted. This is obviously problematic and discourages people from embedding line-specific
 46→                   GitHub permalinks in their docs.
 47→                """.trimIndent()
